36
00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:08.070
So, either a consumer purchases
zero items or one items,

37
00:02:08.070 --> 00:02:10.760
but no consumers want to purchase more.

38
00:02:10.760 --> 00:02:13.970
If we decrease the price to nothing,

39
00:02:13.970 --> 00:02:17.700
every consumer will take at
most one product and use them.

40
00:02:17.700 --> 00:02:20.570
Is the price of 6.5 still optimal,

