00:02:20.570 --> 00:02:24.530
that the price we found in our previous
lecture that maximizes the profit.

42
00:02:24.530 --> 00:02:26.170
The answer is actually yes.

43
00:02:26.170 --> 00:02:31.450
If you think about it, there's no change
in the demand function of the graph or

44
00:02:31.450 --> 00:02:35.220
the revenue table we generated,
